Hi All,

Wondering why the blog is not showing by default in the block body. What I am only seeing is an empty drag and drop (dnd_area_. Is there any declaration I need to put to make the image module attach by default?

```{% block body %}
  {% dnd_area "dnd_area"
    label="Body Section",
    class="hbpage-container"
  %}
  {% module "linked_image" path="@HubSpot/linked_image" %}
    {% dnd_section %}
      {% dnd_column %}
        {% dnd_row %}
          {% module "linked_image" path="@HubSpot/linked_image" %}
        {% end_dnd_row %}
      {% end_dnd_column %}
    {% end_dnd_section %}
  {% end_dnd_area %}
{% endblock body %}```
